As part of the Future STEM Leaders Programme 2025 Cohort 1, another successful Introduction to Telescope and Innovation Session was conducted to inspire young minds in the field of astronomy. The session was led by Md Ebadat Hossian, Deputy Director of Novotheatre Rajshahi, who shared practical knowledge, innovative ideas, and hands-on insights related to telescope use and astronomical exploration. Participants were encouraged to think creatively, ask questions, and explore how innovation plays a vital role in scientific discovery. The interactive discussion sparked curiosity and broadened perspectives on observational astronomy and STEM learning. Organized under the proud banner of SheSTEM and BSCF, the session reflected a continued commitment to nurturing future leaders, fostering innovation, and empowering the next generation of changemakers in science and beyond through meaningful learning experiences.
